org.sql: SELECT reactions.reactable_id FROM reactions WHERE reactions.category = "$1" AND reactions.user_id = "$2" AND reactions.reactable_type = "$3" AND reactions.status <> "$4" ORDER BY reactions.created_at DESC

rewrites.sql: SELECT reactions.reactable_id FROM reactions WHERE reactions.category = "$1" AND reactions.user_id = "$2" AND reactions.reactable_type = "$3" AND reactions.status <> "$4" ORDER BY reactions.created_at DESC LIMIT 1
